name: ExtensionCoverageEligibilityRequest_Item
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `CoverageEligibilityRequest.item` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `CoverageEligibilityRequest.item`, but has no comparisons.
